WEBVTT

00:02.045 --> 00:03.568
Previously on "Queen Sugar"...

00:03.612 --> 00:05.048
How would you feel about me
going deeper into politics?

00:05.092 --> 00:06.441
I'm riding with you.

00:06.484 --> 00:08.573
I told you I got you.
I'm gonna be by later.

00:08.617 --> 00:10.314
Got something real good for you,
alright?

00:10.358 --> 00:11.663
Clerk: This is you
and your wife's

00:11.707 --> 00:13.709
fourth payday loan
in the last six months.

00:13.752 --> 00:16.016
Nova: This work can make people
understand what

00:16.059 --> 00:18.018
"defund the police"
really means.

00:18.061 --> 00:21.064
White folks who don't live here
can't just steal our vaccines.

00:21.108 --> 00:22.674
I called you here
to keep the peace.

00:22.718 --> 00:24.850
You ought to stop trying
to ruin cops' lives.

00:24.894 --> 00:26.983
-Hey!
-Don't do this, man!

00:27.027 --> 00:31.553
♪♪

00:31.596 --> 00:34.512
[ Sighs ] Been at this hospital
all night.

00:34.556 --> 00:36.166
Sure you don't want me
to take you home?

00:36.210 --> 00:38.212
No, I'm okay.
Thank you.

00:38.255 --> 00:39.691
When we gonna
hear something?

00:39.735 --> 00:43.739
The doctor's gonna come out soon
and give us an update.

00:43.782 --> 00:46.089
Can we go see him?

00:46.133 --> 00:48.309
Can't go in his room.

00:48.352 --> 00:50.659
Can only look at him
from the hallway.

00:53.227 --> 00:55.098
Called his daughter yet?

00:55.142 --> 00:56.491
Where she live at again?

00:56.534 --> 00:57.883
Chicago.

00:57.927 --> 01:01.322
I called, Billy, and she said
she was flying in.

01:01.365 --> 01:02.975
What'd you tell her?

01:03.019 --> 01:05.065
The truth.

01:05.108 --> 01:09.678
That her father
was seriously injured.

01:09.721 --> 01:13.421
In a medically
induced coma.

01:13.464 --> 01:15.597
Trying to keep the swelling
in the brain down

01:15.640 --> 01:18.774
to hopefully not have
any permanent damage.

01:18.817 --> 01:20.558
Hey, Vi.

01:20.602 --> 01:22.256
Vi.

01:22.299 --> 01:24.214
He's gonna be
alright.

