♪♪

39:41.901 --> 39:49.517
♪♪

39:49.561 --> 39:57.264
♪♪

39:57.307 --> 39:58.874
No.

39:58.918 --> 40:07.796
♪♪

40:07.840 --> 40:09.711
[ Sighs ]

40:09.755 --> 40:11.713
[ Door opens ]

40:11.757 --> 40:14.412
Ralph Angel.

40:18.459 --> 40:20.505
Mr. Prosper.

40:20.548 --> 40:21.636
What's wrong?

40:21.680 --> 40:27.903
♪♪

40:27.947 --> 40:29.818
It's my baby girl.

40:29.862 --> 40:37.739
♪♪

40:37.783 --> 40:39.480
Wanted you to
see her first.

40:41.787 --> 40:43.266
Remember you talking about

40:43.310 --> 40:46.444
carrying around
Billie's pictures.

40:46.487 --> 40:49.272
Said it was a blessing.

40:49.316 --> 40:53.755
You're gonna love your baby girl
better than I loved mine.

40:53.799 --> 40:58.499
'Cause you're gonna show her
you love her every single day.

41:00.458 --> 41:03.852
Ain't over till it's over,
Mr. Prosper.

41:03.896 --> 41:06.986
You still got time.

41:10.119 --> 41:13.166
We can both show them
what we want to show them.

41:16.430 --> 41:19.128
Right?

41:19.172 --> 41:22.349
I'd like that.

41:22.392 --> 41:23.655
Maybe so.

41:23.698 --> 41:25.439
You never know.

41:29.008 --> 41:32.011
That's right.

41:32.054 --> 41:33.882
Never know.

